ical; featurePoint=Android platform component lifecycle such as service, receiver, provider, or application.\",\n2044:       \"status\": \"platform-replaced\",\n2045:       \"plannedPhase\": \"phase-01-project-skeleton-resources\",\n2046:       \"sourceBehavior\": \"Source app/build.gradle.kts configures an Android application/activity app with Compose, Hilt, and splash dependencies that feed the Android lifecycle entry path.\",\n2047:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The HarmonyOS entry module replaces Android application/plugin lifecycle wiring with a UIAbility/AbilityStage module packaged through cjpm, module.json5, and AppScope metadata.\",\n2048:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\n2049:         \"Manual code/config review: entry/cjpm.toml defines the ohos_app_cangjie_entry package name and build profile used for the HarmonyOS entry module instead of Android Gradle application wiring.\",\n2050:         \"Manual code/config review: AppScope/app.json5 binds the translated bundleName, and entry/src/main/module.json5 wires the module srcEntry and mainElement to the HarmonyOS ability shell that replaces Android lifecycle registration.\",\n2051:         \"Build verification: D:/workspace/Foodike/translation-inputs/build-reports/phase-01-project-skeleton-resources/build-report.json recorded a passed build gate for the phase-01 skeleton.\"\n2052:       ],\n2053:       \"parityLevel\": \"platform-replaced\",\n2054:       \"targetEndpoints\": [\n2055:         \"entry/cjpm.toml::name\",\n2056:         \"entry/cjpm.toml::profile.build.combined.ohos_app_cangjie_entry\",\n2057:         \"AppScope/app.json5::bundleName\",\n2058:         \"entry/src/main/module.json5::srcEntry\",\n2059:         \"entry/src/main/module.json5::mainElement\"\n2060:       ],\n2061:       \"tests\": [],\n2062:       \"notes\": \"Platform replacement is intentional: HarmonyOS package metadata and entry-module ability wiring replace Android application/plugin lifecycle configuration with field-level eviden